HEADWORD: Chamfret
<hw>Cham"fret</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Chamfron</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Carp.)</fld> <def>A small
